README

A Gentoo overlay by viralex (alessandro.rosetti@gmail.com)

Setting up layman

Edit /etc/layman/layman.cfg:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
overlays  : http://www.gentoo.org/proj/en/overlays/layman-global.txt
            https://raw.githubusercontent.com/viralex/viralex-overlay/master/list.xml

and add the overlay using layman.
	layman -f
	layman -a viralex
